data.title: Patti LaBelle Live in Brooklyn, Coney Island Amphitheater
data.meta_description: Join us for an unforgettable evening of music and celebration as Rise Up NYC proudly presents the legendary Patti LaBelle!
data.text:
Join us for an unforgettable evening of music and celebration as Rise Up NYC proudly presents the legendary Patti LaBelle! This iconic artist will take the stage on August 8th at Coney Island Amphitheater in Brooklyn for a night filled with soulful melodies and electrifying performances.

About Patti LaBelle

Known as the Godmother of Soul, Patti LaBelle has been captivating audiences for decades with her powerful voice and dynamic stage presence. With classic hits like “Lady Marmalade,” “If Only You Knew,” and “On My Own,” Patti LaBelle’s performance is set to be a highlight of the summer.
